    <body>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="large-12 columns">
                <a class="button small radius success" href="/admin">Disgo Adminpanel</a>
                <h1>Disgo</h1>
                <p>To enable Disgo on your page, add the following line to your website:</p>
                <input onClick="this.select();" type="text" value="&lt;script src=&quot;{{.}}js/disgo.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;"/>
                <p>Add a comments section by providing an element with a data-disgo-url attribute. Example:</p>

                <span class="hl kwa">&lt;div</span> <span class="hl kwb">data-disgo-url</span>=<span class="hl str">&quot;http://example.com/2014/04/01/facebook-buys-golang&quot;</span><span class="hl kwa">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
